    <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
        Features
    </Paragraph>

    <List Margin="25,0,0,0">
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Timeline control is a Syncfusion control used to select the time frame ranges. </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>It will provide us set of data that is falling inside the selected range.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>It includes the ViewPort to select the limited data.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>The ViewPort can be dragged and dropped at any position inside the TimeLineControl.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
    </List>

    <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
        Interactive Features</Paragraph>

    <List Margin="25,0,0,0">

        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>By clicking and dragging the
                <Bold>"ViewPort"</Bold> the selected range of data is visible.
            </Paragraph>
        </ListItem>    

    </List>

